  "2026-03-07T20:32:24.476Z",maintainer-agent,"Planned change-set: harden dynamic extension command loose-option parsing in src/cli/main.ts by rejecting unsafe prototype-related keys and using a null-prototype map; add unit tests to lock deterministic behavior and guard against prototype-pollution vectors."
  "2026-03-07T20:34:35.159Z",maintainer-agent,"Implemented docs-first contract updates in PRD/README for extension loose-option parser hardening, extracted parser into src/cli/extension-command-options.ts, and added focused unit coverage in tests/unit/main-loose-options.spec.ts for deterministic parsing plus unsafe-key rejection."
